{"tid":1630980,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"旅遊作家項明生挑戰「雙面人」極限 被揭Facebook/微博兩個立場 中港粉絲齊鬧爆","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T02:00:51.000Z","uid":68738,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2e1ac401591db7fbe1ca4ac29e0166a70f768107","tid":1630980,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:19:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KT58ZU4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKT58ZU4.png&h=66c6894f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旅遊作家項明生挑戰「雙面人」極限 被揭Facebook/微博兩個立場 中港粉絲齊鬧爆<br />\n<br />\n我們近日都看到不少人在網上表態，有人愛國護旗，就引來香港抗爭者鄙視；有人表明立場撐示威者，就換來大陸粉絲鬧爆不愛國。有人真心有人假意，但最緊要揀定立場。不過旅遊作家兼旅遊節目主持項明生就夠威，在facebook/IG出遊行相撐示威者嘲蒙面法，當你以為他是撐香港抗爭者的時候。有人就發現原來在微博，他不只拍片唱〈我的祖國〉，還在831時分享文章：「今日民陣遊行雖然收檔，但前車可鑪，或有人會借『行街』之名生事，加上警方昨日收網，或再有人生亂。未雨綢繆，支持警方戒備，隨時執法！」現在同時被香港、大陸粉絲分別於facebook、微博鬧爆，絕對創先河。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gz9qhHx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGz9qhHx.png&h=e21f154d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大量中港粉絲同時鬧爆「雙面人」、「精神分裂」之後昨晚深夜他就在facebook出回應，說到：「我就是我，我是香港人，也是中國人，更是地球村人。我會繼續為香港人發聲，全力支持民主自由法治的追求，終身追求普世價值。」亦解釋：「我的微博戶口由一個專業團隊管理，每次貼文，並非由本人親自撰寫及轉發。由於內地有網絡法規管，微博貼文自然不能照抄Facebook人容。所以，並不存在『兩家茶禮』、『雙面人』之說。」<br />\n<br />\n但有網民就質疑，就算文章是「專業團隊」撰寫，那唱肉緊唱〈我的祖國〉的是他吧，他在片中就說：「係之前錄嘅，因為一啲知名人仕都會唱愛國歌表示愛國。」<br />\n現在，香港粉絲鬧爆：「你支持警方執法喎，仲死撐？X你啦雙面獸。」「愛國同奶共係兩件事，其實冇得逼人歸邊，正如小粉紅亦不能逼你愛黨。我地呢個年紀好多都係大中華膠，不過你唱嗰首歌都真係幾難頂。」「831是香港人的痛，不可以拿來講笑。」<br />\n<br />\n大陸粉絲則同時鬧爆：「聽說你還在臉書上解釋：『我的微博有專業團隊打理，並非本人所寫。』但那首歌是不是也是別人貼著你的人皮面具唱的？」「你個賤婦！」「兩面人，自以為聰明，以為兩邊都看不到？」「發去黃營，他們也不喜歡雙面人，會被起底和騷擾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/article/9Rk72m?utm_source=copyshare&amp;fbclid=IwAR1E9tQRsN0Br4hb1ufhFcFOqxIgfxP81Ad_mAnd9mw6UX1ZfCGydwixb3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Farticle%2F9Rk72m%3Futm_source%3Dcopyshare%26fbclid%3DIwAR1E9tQRsN0Br4hb1ufhFcFOqxIgfxP81Ad_mAnd9mw6UX1ZfCGydwixb3s&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6kcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=0f4db8c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/article/9Rk72m?utm_source=copyshare&amp;fbclid=IwAR1E9tQRsN0Br4hb1ufhFcFOqxIgfxP81Ad_mAnd9mw6UX1ZfCGydwixb3s</a>"},{"pid":"bcea0bbd01dd50726dd95dd8d59106947e7b366a","tid":1630980,"uid":93986,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:49:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然不嬲冇留意呢條gay佬<br />\n但估唔到咁肉酸"},{"pid":"064593720030b3464a46cd388c5b7f62f0d21efd","tid":1630980,"uid":555,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:08:02.000Z","msg":"聽都未撚聽過"},{"pid":"975de707abba34574c6fca54f5e0a103854b0561","tid":1630980,"uid":217411,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:33:57.000Z","msg":"佢之前有單非禮案 <br />\n之後多謝黑警還清白<br />\n大家明喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e67e9735a5ccd3c249aa9383e1d3dc7e3e27c3","tid":1630980,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:35:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af12cbd4f77efdac98dee6975b575ea6f785f930","tid":1630980,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:35:13.000Z","msg":"賤gay佬"},{"pid":"56950f6382b946e2ad7581f8c2809cbaf0300aac","tid":1630980,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:36:42.000Z","msg":"who?"},{"pid":"c3f18535373bb2d494e164e47e781addb7c22559","tid":1630980,"uid":116967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:33:28.000Z","msg":"係咪on9到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f44f47ad2dbb2b4a9356d385bc3a6063c9a734","tid":1630980,"uid":33077,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:10.000Z","msg":"佢係大陸黎架"},{"pid":"b7dd806c53f20abb43cc163d5752ab7e3b095e62","tid":1630980,"uid":33077,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:53.000Z","msg":"核撚突 仲核突過d 藍扮黃食店"},{"pid":"08162313d2a5e3dcd6d5658eb81d7faacfe1933a","tid":1630980,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:17:00.000Z","msg":"嚴打呢啲人"},{"pid":"3dc750a796b989af06fbdd89254d12742d9cf01d","tid":1630980,"uid":33077,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:19:42.000Z","msg":"呢個真真正正 正宗<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">陰陽屎忽鬼</span></strong>"},{"pid":"ee9779c2c013447fa53ca21364a2a178ebaa78bc","tid":1630980,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:27:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d1c659a6d55f34cbec0bc563392b95d11de7512","tid":1630980,"uid":73381,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:48:05.000Z","msg":"死gay佬又要娶老婆 唔怪得佢可以做出依啲雙面行為嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15750b1be1cd6f582bbbdb702883438726693628","tid":1630980,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:54:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d0d0f8bb808fe5fb3716fac53384bc2f3ec387a","tid":1630980,"uid":49316,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:29:23.000Z","msg":"N 年前睇壹週刋訪問。佢好強調自己新移民被歧視 聽得出上位後有笑鳩香港人唔夠佢叻<br />\n<br />\n宜家想食兩家茶禮。我諗支那人會有意見多D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5963eabfbf0b9ffaacc5b5f67f200b61a41842