陸粉絲則同時鬧爆：「聽說你還在臉書上解釋：『我的微博有專業團隊打理，並非本人所寫。』但那首歌是不是也是別人貼著你的人皮面具唱的？」「你個賤婦！」「兩面人，自以為聰明，以為兩邊都看不到？」「發去黃營，他們也不喜歡雙面人，會被起底和騷擾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/article/9Rk72m?utm_source=copyshare&amp;fbclid=IwAR1E9tQRsN0Br4hb1ufhFcFOqxIgfxP81Ad_mAnd9mw6UX1ZfCGydwixb3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Farticle%2F9Rk72m%3Futm_source%3Dcopyshare%26fbclid%3DIwAR1E9tQRsN0Br4hb1ufhFcFOqxIgfxP81Ad_mAnd9mw6UX1ZfCGydwixb3s&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6kcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=0f4db8c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/article/9Rk72m?utm_source=copyshare&amp;fbclid=IwAR1E9tQRsN0Br4hb1ufhFcFOqxIgfxP81Ad_mAnd9mw6UX1ZfCGydwixb3s</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:26:35.000Z","msg":"微博個ac係咪真<br />\n條link係content farm"},{"pid":"7371876e0c6697fef07c0b187b19ca3cdd0356e5","tid":1630980,"uid":76098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:44:46.000Z","msg":"一直睇呢條撚屌唔順眼"},{"pid":"5af30cceb0beee41c68fcd1d8057a56d1bbb6cc1","tid":1630980,"uid":76632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:14:57.000Z","msg":"佢家吓黃絲帶，又變返做藍絲帶。"},{"pid":"28cd9a872405d9bade5191bac00f962e2ea44d78","tid":1630980,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b807b47d1306c8261ef788c458fdbf12e7bef4ab","tid":1630980,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:15:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">8</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">提款日</span></span></strong><br />\n各大銀行總行撳錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1634001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1634001</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"fon